Package com.theeyetribe.clientsdk

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ICalibrationProcessHandler
    Callback interface with methods associated to Calibration process.
    ICalibrationResultListener
    Callback interface with methods associated to the changes to calibration state.
    IConnectionStateListener
    Callback interface with methods associated to the current state of the connection to the EyeTribe Server.
    IGazeListener
    Callback interface with methods associated to gaze estimation updates.
    IScreenStateListener
    Callback interface with methods associated to the currently active calibration screen in a multi screen setup.
    ITrackerStateListener
    Callback interface with methods associated to the state of the physical Tracker device.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GazeManager
    GazeManager is the main entry point of the EyeTribe Java SDK.

    EyeTribe API constants
